ENTRY            D1081   20251216   20260508   20260508       D151
SUBENT        D1081001   20251216   20260508   20260508       D151
BIB                 12         29
TITLE      Nuclear reaction dynamics in 12C+120Sn collisions
AUTHOR     (L.Garrido-Gomez, J.P.Fernandez-Garcia, M.A.G.Alvarez,
            L.M.Martinis, J.K.L.Chaves, W.A.Y.Hatano,
            V.Scarduelli, L.R.Gasques, L.C.Chamon, J.Gomez,
            B.Paes, A.Arazi)
REFERENCE  (J,PR/C,112,064602,2025)
INSTITUTE  (2SPNSEU,3BZLUSP,3ARGCNE,3ARGCIN)
FACILITY   (VDGT,3BZLUSP) 8 MV Pelletron accelerator
SAMPLE     Two samples tilted at 30 deg relative to beam direction
           . 120Sn (~300 ug/cm2)
           . 120Sn (~300 ug/cm2) + Au (50 ug/cm2)
DETECTOR   (TELES,SISD,SISD) Two large area telescopes (50 x
            50 mm2) covering theta(lab) from ~84 to 161 deg.
           Each telescope composed of
           . two 20 um single-sided Si strip telescopes segmented
             into 16 vertical strips serving as dE detectors
           . two 300 um SSSSD detectors segmented into 16
             horizontal strips serving as E detectors
           (SIBAR) Two Si surface barrier detectors at 30 and
            50 deg to detect elastic scattering of 12C with 120Sn
            and 197Au
           (SIBAR) Five Si surface barrier detectors at 60, 90,
            150, 160 and 170 deg
METHOD     (EDE)
ANALYSIS   (NTRTH)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) purely statistical
STATUS     (APRVD) Proofread by Lucas Garrido Gomez (2025-12-17)
HISTORY    (20251216R) On. Data received from Lucas Garrido Gomez.
           (20251216C) On
ENDBIB              29
